3.text: Manuka: Hey, don't put that pen in your mouth.
3.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>: Hey, don't put that pen in your mouth.</prosody></speak>

4.text: Manuka's Sister: Why can't I? This is my new pen!
4.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>'s Sister: Why can't I? This is my new pen!</prosody></speak>

5.text: Manuka: No, it's not. That's my black pen and those are my colour pencils too!
5.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>: No, it's not. That's my black pen and those are my colour pencils too!</prosody></speak>

6.text: Manuka's Sister: Oh well, these are not yours. These colour pencils are mine.
6.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>'s Sister: Oh well, these are not yours. These colour pencils are mine.</prosody></speak>

7.text: Manuka: No, those colour pencils are mine and that pen is also mine.
7.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>: No, those colour pencils are mine and that pen is also mine.</prosody></speak>

8.text: Manuka's Sister: No they are mine!
8.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>'s Sister: No they are mine!</prosody></speak>

9.text: Manuka: Don't shout. Let's not fight about this.
9.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>: Don't shout. Let's not fight about this.</prosody></speak>

10.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>'s Sister: Hm….. Alright.</prosody></speak>

11.text: Manuka: Let me see, is this yours? Does it have your name on it?
11.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>: Let me see, is this yours? Does it have your name on it?</prosody></speak>

12.text: Manuka's Sister: Ummm. No it doesn't .
12.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>'s Sister: Ummm. No it doesn't.</prosody></speak>

13.text: Manuka: Then, this is my pen and those are my colour pencils. Maybe, your colour pencils are in your bag.
13.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>: Then, this is my pen and those are my colour pencils. Maybe, your colour pencils are in your bag.</prosody></speak>

14.text: Manuka's Sister: Let me see…ah, yes, they are here. Sorry!
14.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='manuka'>Manuka</phoneme>'s Sister: Let me see…ah, yes, they are here. Sorry!</prosody></speak>
